<taxonomicName class="Insecta" genus="A." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="A. fasciale" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciale">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">A. fasciale</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Hampson, 1896) have recently been found in southeast China by 
<bibRefCitation author="Wu, J" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Northeast Forestry University" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" pagination="144 - 147" refId="B31" refString="Wu, J, Zhao, TT, Han, HL, 2020. Two new records species of the Tribe Araeopteronini (Erebidae: Boletobiinae) from China. Journal of Northeast Forestry University 48 (5): 144 - 147" title="Two new records species of the Tribe Araeopteronini (Erebidae: Boletobiinae) from China." volume="48" year="2020">Wu et al. (2020)</bibRefCitation>
. Three further new 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hampson" authorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Araeopteron" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Araeopteron" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">Araeopteron</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species are described below.
</paragraph>
